1.01.name: wordpress/fighting-the-lyrics
1.01.description: Got tired of Hello Dolly lyrics, and being a Peter Gabriel fan, wrote this instead. You can upload multiple .txt files containing lyrics, follow a naming convention to display artist, album and song name, together with a line from the lyrics.
